{# ── Kinetic drawing module ──────────────────────────────────────── #}
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
  <h3 class="font-avenir font-bold text-2xl">Kinetic drawing module.</h3>
  <p class="font-inter text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
    Children traced pre-defined shapes on screen with a finger. Micro variations in
    that movement were the data. The module needed to be gamified to keep young
    children engaged, without introducing difficulty that would skew the results.
  </p>

