{# ── Kinetic movement module ─────────────────────────────────────── #}
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
  <h3 class="font-avenir font-bold text-2xl">Kinetic movement module.</h3>
  <p class="font-inter text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
    Children followed a sinusoidal arm movement pattern while watching a screen they
    were also moving around. The challenge was keeping instruction visible and readable
    during large physical movements.
  </p>
  <p class="font-inter text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
    The most important part of this design was the instructional animation I produced
    in After Effects. Speed to testing was more important than polish here, so I used
    my own voiceover and basic music to keep the project moving.
  </p>

